tyle=\"opacity: 0.01; left: 534px; top: 1856.81px;\"> <div id=\":xs\" class=\"T-I J-J5-Ji aQv T-I-ax7 L3 a5q\" title=\"Download\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Download attachment \" data-tooltip-class=\"a1V\"> <div class=\"aSK J-J5-Ji aYr\"></div> </div> </div> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width:100%;border-collapse:collapse\"> <tbody class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnTextBlockOuter\"> <tr> <td valign=\"top\" class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"padding-top:9px\"> <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;min-width:100%;border-collapse:collapse\" width=\"100%\" class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnTextContentContainer\"> <tbody> <tr> <td valign=\"top\" class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:18px;padding-bottom:9px;padding-left:18px;word-break:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:'Source Sans Pro','Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:150%;text-align:left\"> <p style=\"margin:10px 0;padding:0;color:#444444;font-family:'Source Sans Pro','Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:150%;text-align:left\"><strong>Have you seen or found anything that surprised you over the season?</strong></p> <p style=\"margin:10px 0;padding:0;color:#444444;font-family:'Source Sans Pro','Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:150%;text-align:left\">I think all of us were surprised by the number of insects we could find just by studying leaves! It is amazing what you find when you take a close look at something. A passerby might not think of a tree teeming with insects or how important they are in an ecosystem food web, but I think it gave us all a new appreciation of our 6- and 8-legged friends!</p> <p style=\"margin:10px 0;padding:0;color:#444444;font-family:'Source Sans Pro','Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:150%;text-align:left\"><strong>What’s the key to your surveying success?&nbsp;</strong></p> <p style=\"margin:10px 0;padding:0;color:#444444;font-family:'Source Sans Pro','Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:150%;text-align:left\">The key to our surveying success definitely lies with our amazing, dedicated volunteers. We would not have been able to get the project off the ground at the nature center without them! Stage Nature Center is run by a small nonprofit group, the Troy Nature Society, and staff hours are limited. Without our passionate and dedicated volunteers, it would be very difficult for us to take on additional projects.</p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnCaptionBlock\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"> <tbody class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnCaptionBlockOuter\"> <tr> <td class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnCaptionBlockInner\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:9px\"> <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnCaptionRightContentOuter\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"> <tbody> <tr> <td valign=\"top\" class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnCaptionRightContentInner\" style=\"padding:0 9px\"> <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnCaptionRightImageContentContainer\" width=\"264\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"> <tbody> <tr> <td class=\"m_-3325922716041993988mcnCaptionRightImageContent\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://ci4.googleusercontent.com/proxy/9PPG-Ed2LcJ9HLtJHwJ6zkVnl8daC-cqDJn5MvGvGxNqm3MPfUi-hBsR9o4PvABqcZugOsf3flks5MWctCJGg-Gs9_dQ7OsoWJvfvKUOwF0WnfNmD9YX927wd9y_-wxkMFfoOmIVrXiQly-VGNZ1rHTJGb9UUJnjJog=s0-d-e1